<HL>
   Marketing &amp; Media:
   Mattel, McDonald's Plan
   `Happy Meals' Promotion
</HL>
<DATE>
08/07/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B4
</SO>
<CO>
   MAT MCD
</CO>
<MS>
CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)
</MS>
